\ls3\ilvl1\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 And he writes this letter in the backdrop of Christians being persecuted for their beliefs. \'a0\uc0\u8232 \
\ls3\ilvl1\kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 In many ways the Christians of that time were mocked and outcasts. \'a0\uc0\u8232 \
